text: Nicktoons () is the Central and Eastern Europe division of Nicktoons. It was released on 15 February 2018 (in Poland), on 1 April 2019 (in Hungary and Romania), on 14 July 2020 in Serbia, Croatia, Slovenia and Albania. ==Programming== ===Current programming=== *ALVINNN!!! and the Chipmunks *Avatar: The Last Airbender *Breadwinners *Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness *Lego City Adventures *Rainbow Butterfly Unicorn Kitty *Sanjay and Craig *SpongeBob SquarePants *Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles *The Fairly OddParents *The Adventures of Kid Danger *The Casagrandes *The Loud House *The Penguins of Madagascar ===Former programming=== *Back at the Barnyard *Bunsen Is a Beast *Danny Phantom *Fanboy and Chum Chum *Get Blake! *Harvey Beaks *Hey Arnold *Mysticons *Pig Goat Banana Cricket *Rabbids Invasion *Rise of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles *The Adventures of Jimmy Neutron: Boy Genius *The Legend of Korra *T.U.F.F.
